%div.alert.alert-warning
  %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-exclamation-sign
  LBMC application error  

%div.pad_below
  The error has been logged in the LBMC system and will be reported to the LBMC development team.

%div.pad_below
  - if session[:token].nil?
    It doesn't look like you are logged in.  You can log in from the 
    %a{ :href => url("/") } LBMC home page
  - else
    %a#new-record.btn.btn-success{ :href => url("/record/new")} 
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-pencil
      Create a New Record


%div.pad_below
  If you continue to see this error, please contact us for help.